O(1)&amp;lt;O(log_2 n)&amp;lt;O(n)&amp;lt;O(nlog_2 n)&amp;lt;O(n^2)&amp;lt;O(n^3)&amp;lt;O(2^n)&amp;lt;O(n!)&amp;lt;O(n^n)
